column3: utACK (with or without **func**), but needs rebase.\n
I'm not sure if it's worth keeping the **func** but I'm not against it.\n
Tend to agree with @jtimon. I think it was removed in other places where information was migrated to the debug message.\n

Agree with removing. I don't think function names are very useful to most debug.log readers, and to those that are, you can just grep the source code for the message. Though perhaps we should do a combined effort of fixing it everywhere. ACK with or without **func**\n
